    <chapter num="3">
        <verse num="1">
            <content> </content>
            <content> Na hwɛ, nna no ne berɛ a mede Yuda ne Yerusalem nnommum bɛsane aba no mu no, </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="2">
            <content> mɛboaboa amanaman nyinaa ano, na mede wɔn bɛsiane aba Yehosafat bonhwa no mu, na me ne wɔn adi asɛm wɔ hɔ, me man ne m’agyapadeɛ Israel a wɔabɔ wɔn apete amanaman mu, na wɔakyɛ m’asase no mu nti. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="3">
            <content> Ɛfiri sɛ wɔtwee me man so ntonto, na wɔde abarimaa gyee odwamamfoɔ, na wɔtɔn abaayewa gyee nsa nomee.</content>
            <content> </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="4">
            <content>Nanso moreyɛ me dɛn, Tiro ne Sidon ne Filistifoɔ amantoɔ nyinaa? Deɛ mayɛ bi na mode rehyɛ me ananmu, anaasɛ mo na moreyɛ me biribie? Ɛherɛ so ntɛm so na mɛdane deɛ moreyɛ no agu mo atifi. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="5">
            <content>Sɛ mofaa me dwetɛ ne me sika, na mode me nnwinneɛ a ɛsɔ ani a ɛyɛ no kɔɔ mo asɔrefie. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="6">
            <content>Na Yuda mma ne Yerusalem mma no, motontɔn wɔn maa Helafoɔ, sɛ moreyi wɔn afiri wɔn asase so akɔ akyirikyiri. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="7">
            <content>Hwɛ, merenyane wɔn na wɔafiri deɛ motontɔn wɔn kɔeɛ hɔ, na mede deɛ moayɛ bɛsane abua mo atifi, </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="8">
            <content>na matontɔn mo mmabanin ne mo mmammaa mahyɛ Yuda mma nsa, na wɔatontɔn wɔn ama Sabafoɔ, akyirikyiri man bi, AWURADE na waka.</content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="9">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Mompae yei amanaman mu,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>monnwira ɔsa ho,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>monnyane nnɔmmarima,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>akofoɔ nyinaa ntwe mpini,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>wɔmforo mmra.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="10">
            <block_quote>
                <content> </content>
                <content> Momfa mo nsɔ mmobɔ mfena,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na momfa mo nnerɛ mmobɔ mpea.</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>Deɛ wahodwo nka sɛ: Meyɛ dɔmmarima.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="11">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Monyɛ ntɛm mmra ɛ,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>mo amanaman a moatwa ahyia nyinaa,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>mommɛhyia!</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>Ɛhɔ na, AWURADE, gya wo nnɔmmarima no bra.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="12">
            <block_quote>
                <content> </content>
                <content> Amanaman nsɔre ntu mmra</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>Yehosafat bonhwa no mu;</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>na ɛhɔ na mɛtena ase abu</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>amanaman a wɔfiri afa nyinaa atɛn.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="13">
            <block_quote>
                <content> </content>
                <content> Momfa kantankrankyi nhyɛ mu,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na deɛ wɔtwa ahoa.</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>Mommra mmɛtiatia so,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na nsa-kyi-amena no ayɛ ma,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>ntɛɛpo no abu so,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na wɔn bɔne adɔɔso.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="14">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Nnipa yuu, nnipa yuu</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>wɔ atemmuo bonhwa no mu;</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE da no abɛn,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>atemmuo bonhwa no mu.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="15">
            <block_quote>
                <content> </content>
                <content> Owia ne ɔsrane aduru sum,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na nsoromma agyae haran.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="16">
            <block_quote>
                <content> </content>
                <content> Na AWURADE firi Sion bobom</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na ɔfiri Yerusalem ma ne nne so,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na ɔsoro ne asase wosowoso;</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>nanso AWURADE yɛ dwanekɔbea ma ne man,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>ne aban a ɛyɛ den ma Israel mma.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="17">
            <block_quote>
                <content> </content>
                <content> Na mobɛhunu sɛ me, AWURADE, mene mo Nyankopɔn</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>a mete Sion, me bepɔ kronkron no so,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>na Yerusalem bɛdane kronkronbea,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na ananafoɔ rentwa mu hɔ bio.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="18">
            <block_quote>
                <content> </content>
                <content> Na ɛda no,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>mmepɔ bɛsosɔ nsamono,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na nkokoɔ asene nufosuo,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>na nsuo asene</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>Yuda mmonhwa nyinaa mu;</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>na nsuo aniwa bɛfiri AWURADE fie</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>asene na akɔfɔ Sitim bonhwa no.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="19">
            <block_quote>
                <content> </content>
                <content> Misraim bɛdane amamfo,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na Edom adane nkyɛkyerɛ afo,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote>
                <content>ɛsiane Yuda mma so atirimuɔdenbɔ no nti,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>ɛfiri sɛ wɔahwie mogya a ɛdi bem agu, wɔn asase so.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="20">
            <block_quote>
                <content>Na Yuda deɛ, wɔbɛtena hɔ daa,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na Yerusalem atena hɔ awoɔ ntoatoasoɔ nyinaa mu.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
        <verse num="21">
            <block_quote>
                <content> </content>
                <content> Na mɛtɔ wɔn mogya so were a mentɔɔɛ no,</content>
            </block_quote>
            <block_quote kind="LEFT_INDENTED">
                <content>na AWURADE bɛtena Sion ara.</content>
            </block_quote>
        </verse>
